### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@itemId = 001

### CREATE - Crear nuevo item
POST {{baseUrl}}/hardware
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{itemId}}",
  "name": "Laptop Dell",
  "quantity": 5,
  "location": "Office A"
}

### READ ALL - Obtener todos los items
GET {{baseUrl}}/hardware

### READ ONE - Obtener un item específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/hardware/{{itemId}}

### UPDATE - Actualizar item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hardware/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3,
  "location": "Office B"
}

### DELETE - Eliminar item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/hardware/{{itemId}}

### CREATE - Otro ejemplo
POST {{baseUrl}}/hardware
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "002",
  "name": "Monitor Samsung",
  "quantity": 10,
  "location": "Warehouse"
}

### Error Test - Sin campos requeridos
POST {{baseUrl}}/hardware
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

GET https://vk6496iyqd.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/prod/hardware
